sailpoint.object

Class AccountSelection.AccountInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • sailpoint.tools.xml.AbstractXmlObject
      • sailpoint.object.AccountSelection.AccountInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, sailpoint.tools.xml.PersistentXmlObject
    Enclosing class:
    AccountSelection

    public static class AccountSelection.AccountInfo
extends AbstractXmlObject
    The distinguishing information about an account. This is stored in the AccountSelection rather than calculated on the fly to allow a relatively dumb form to be able to consume it.

    A list of these represents the possible target accounts that can be selected.
